  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are going to examine whether oxytocin has a prokinetic effect on gastric
      emptying in patients suffering from gastro paresis. Oxytocin infusion will be compared with
      sodium chloride infusion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are going to examine whether oxytocin has a prokinetic effect on gastric
      emptying in patients suffering from gastro paresis. Oxytocin infusion will be compared with
      sodium chloride infusion.The gastric emptying is estimade by sitntigraphy during 70 minutes,
      and performed twicw. Once with saline and once with oxytocin.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
